Pikmin Arcade Game
- similar concept to Pac-Man
- maze structure, avoid enemies, collect "nectar"
Requirements:
- Game must allow playable Pikmin choice
- Game should track score
- Game can display current score during gameplay
- Game should give player 3 "lives"
- If player sprite touches enemy, -1 life
- If all 3 lives gone, game over/game ends
- Player should be able to move up, down, left, right
- Player can enter name to associate with score
- Each collected "nectar" must correspond to 1 point (+1 to score)
- Game must only support one player at a time
